ABI Signals Concerns on C&W Worldwide Pay, Changes, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-04T21:36:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/abi-signals-concerns-on-c-w-worldwide-pay-changes-ft-reports.html
Cable & Wireless Worldwide Plc (CW/)  may be
challenged by its shareholders after the  Association of British
Insurers  issued a so-called “amber-top alert” to shareholders
to signal its concerns about C&W Worldwide pay policy for top
executives and the recent boardroom changes, which came just
after the company issued a profit warning last week, the
Financial Times reported, without attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 